desc_long								关于这款游戏							We have been waiting for you commander. The Dzerhgan forces are amassing an offensive force to strike our newest colony on Jernae 2. Gather your crew as there is no time to waste! We need these alien scum to realize they should look elsewhere if they want easy pickens.  Starship: Nova Strike is a side scrolling action game that will draw you into its universe and captivate you for hours. Can you save an entire colony from destruction and send the alien invaders fleeing to their homeland?						
